# This file lists the devices that should be check for connection to the local
# network.  When the connection status of one of these devices changes the
# main script with notify the Smartthing application specified.  One device
# per line.  Lines starting with a # are ignored.
#
# Line format: name,mac,appid,token
#
# name  - A friendly name for this device
# mac   - The mac address to look for in the routers list of devices
# appid - The Smartthings published Application ID (from the IDE)
# token - The Smartthings Application AuthZ token
#
###############################################################################
